{
  "group_title": "获取会话状态",
  "api_name": "get",
  "method": "POST",
  "api_url": "https://qyapi.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/kf/service_state/get",
  "description": "从微信用户发起咨询到会话结束，该次会话可能会经过不同状态流转。企业或第三方可使用API获取会话状态。",
  "query_params": [
    {
      "name": "access_token",
      "type": "string",
      "required": true,
      "description": "调用接口凭证"
    }
  ],
  "body_params": [
    {
      "name": "open_kfid",
      "type": "string",
      "required": true,
      "description": "客服账号ID"
    },
    {
      "name": "external_userid",
      "type": "string",
      "required": true,
      "description": "微信客户的external_userid"
    }
  ],
  "response_params": [
    {
      "name": "errcode",
      "type": "int32",
      "required": false,
      "description": "返回码"
    },
    {
      "name": "errmsg",
      "type": "string",
      "required": false,
      "description": "错误码描述"
    },
    {
      "name": "service_state",
      "type": "int32",
      "required": false,
      "description": "当前的会话状态，状态定义参考概述中的表格"
    },
    {
      "name": "servicer_userid",
      "type": "string",
      "required": false,
      "description": "接待人员的userid。第三方应用为密文userid，即open_userid。仅当state=3时有效"
    }
  ],
  "request_examples": [
    {
      "title": "请求示例",
      "language": "json",
      "code": "{\n\t\"open_kfid\": \"wkxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx\",\n\t\"external_userid\": \"wmxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx\"\n}"
    }
  ],
  "response_examples": [
    {
      "title": "返回示例",
      "language": "json",
      "code": "{\n    \"errcode\": 0,\n    \"errmsg\": \"ok\",\n\t\"service_state\": 3,\n\t\"servicer_userid\": \"zhangsan\"\n}"
    }
  ],
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "权限说明",
      "content": "调用的应用需要满足如下的权限：\n- 自建应用: 配置到「微信客服- 可调用接口的应用」中\n- 第三方应用: 具有“微信客服->管理账号、分配会话和收发消息”权限\n- 代开发自建应用: 具有“微信客服->管理账号、分配会话和收发消息”权限\n\n*注：* 从2023年12月1日0点起，不再支持通过系统应用secret调用接口，存量企业暂不受影响 [查看详情](https://developer.work.weixin.qq.com/document/51165)"
    }
  ]
}